                <head>8. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On January 7–8, the Government of Israel announced a further troop withdrawal to
                    a line roughly following the meridian 33 degrees 44 minutes, leaving no Israeli
                    forces west of El Arish in the Sinai Peninsula. (Report by the Secretary-General
                    on compliance with General Assembly resolutions calling for withdrawal of troops
                    and other measures, January 15; U.N. doc. <gloss target="#t_A1"
                    >A</gloss>/3500)</p>
            </div>
